text: Yallat agleytit hayte koros (makki koros kinnuk) Yalli dubuk kaa naqbudem nek faxinnay nee kee nabbobti kaak sa tu aqbudak mananninooy, usuk carammoyse weemik tu carammoysak manannino itte, keenik duma sugte koros tamannah abteeh, tamannah itteh ten usun wohut dirab acayuk, tokkel Yalli ken finqiseh, toysa Yallih farmoytiitil baxxaqqa le gudduysiyyak sa maca taniih? tu matan
